      <title>前牛银雨人纳赫塔（Naheta）挑选了巴克特（Bakkt）的周转努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/akshay-naheta-picked-as-co-ceo-to-head-bakkt-s-turnaround-efforts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前软银集团官员Akshay Naheta负责监督其一些最大的交易，他已加入Bakkt Holdings Inc.担任联合主持的执行官，以帮助扭转陷入困境的美国加密货币贸易和监护平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/akshay-naheta-picked-as-co-ceo-to-head-bakkt-s-turnaround-efforts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 04:23:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
