      <title>FT说，NVIDIA计划在美国制造的电子产品上进行大规模支出。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/nvidia-will-spend-hundreds-of-billions-on-chips-made-in-us-ft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《金融时报》报道，NVIDIA Corp.的目标是在未来四年内花费数亿美元来购买美国制造的筹码和电子产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/nvidia-will-spend-hundreds-of-billions-on-chips-made-in-us-ft</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 03:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
